      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You have seriously got to see this beauty in person. It is in absolutely stunning condition\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, and it drives like an absolute dream. It\u2019s super clean, inside and out, and ready for its next adventure. If you're looking for perfection on wheels, this is definitely the one for you. Drop me a message, I'd love to chat more about it!",
      "price": 44500.0,
