    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional vehicle that redefines the term 'showroom quality.' This car has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment, shielded from the elements since day one. The exterior paint retains its deep, factory luster with a professional ceramic coating and is entirely free of rock chips, swirls, or imperfections. Inside, the cabin remains in pristine condition; the premium leather upholstery shows zero signs of bolster wear or creasing, and the original protective floor mats have kept the carpeting immaculate. Every electronic feature, from the high-fidelity sound system to the advanced driver assistance suite, operates exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, boasting a comprehensive service history performed exclusively by certified technicians. It drives with the tightness and precision of a brand-new vehicle. This sale includes all original documentation, two factory keys, and a custom-fitted car cover. For the discerning buyer who accepts nothing less than perfection, this is the one.",
      "price": 43900.0,
